timeDropDown()

Description
    string timeDropDown(array $attPairs [, object $engine = NULL])
    Builds the appropriate markup for displaying a drop-down pre-populated time form.

Parameters
    attPairs
	An array containing attribute pairs, $attPairs['formname'], $attPairs['separator'], $attPairs['hourformat'], $attPairs['mininterval'], $attPairs
	['settime'].
    engine
	The engine object.

Return Values
    Returns a string value containing the proper markup and data to build the drop-down time menu.

See Also
    dateDropDown
